                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </a>
          <hr class="border-warm-200">
          <a href="/resources/ai-search-stack-guide/" class="block group">
            <p class="text-base text-zunkiree-600 group-hover:text-zunkiree-700 leading-snug mb-2">
              The AI Search Stack for the Modern Enterprise
