</section>

{# CONTENT SECTION #}
<section class="relative bg-white px-4 md:px-6 py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16">

      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">What you'll learn</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            In this 45-minute session, our engineering team demonstrates a complete AI search implementation from scratch. Watch as we transform a basic keyword search into a conversational AI experience that understands natural language queries.
          </p>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This is not a product demo. It's a technical walkthrough with live coding, real API calls, and practical tips from engineers who have built AI search systems for production environments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">Webinar agenda</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 font-medium">0:00</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-warm-black">Introduction & Setup</p>
                <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm">Environment setup and project overview</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 font-medium">5:00</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-warm-black">API Walkthrough</p>
                <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm">Understanding the Zunkiree Search API structure</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 font-medium">15:00</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-warm-black">Live Coding: Basic Integration</p>
                <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm">Building your first AI search query</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 font-medium">25:00</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-warm-black">Advanced Patterns</p>
                <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm">Context handling, follow-up queries, and error handling</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 font-medium">35:00</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-warm-black">Production Tips</p>
                <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm">Caching, monitoring, and performance optimization</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 font-medium">40:00</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-warm-black">Q&A Session</p>
                <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm">Answers to common implementation questions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">What you get:</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {% for item in resource.whatYouGet %}
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 mt-1">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">{{ item }}</span>
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">About the presenter</h2>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gray-200 flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-warm-black">Dr. Emily Rodriguez</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm mb-2">AI Research Lead, Zunkiree Labs</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm">Emily leads AI research at Zunkiree Labs, focusing on natural language understanding and semantic search. She has implemented AI search systems for Fortune 500 companies and startups alike.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5" data-reveal>
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          {% set formTitle = resource.formTitle %}
          {% set ctaText = resource.ctaText %}
          {% include "components/lead-capture-form.njk" %}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

